OL,3,CBBC reporter tells court she took
OL,4,C'utmost care' with Adams allegation
OL,6,FMr Adams is suing the BBC over what he
OL,7,Fhas called a "grievous smear" included
OL,8,Fin a documentary that alleged he
OL,9,Fsanctioned the killing of a former
OL,10,FSinn Fein official revealed to be an
OL,11,Finformer.
OL,13,FHe claims a BBC Spotlight programme,
OL,14,Fand an accompanying online story,
OL,15,Fdefamed him by alleging he sanctioned
OL,16,Fthe killing of Denis Donaldson. He
OL,17,Fdenies any involvement.
OL,19,FMr Donaldson was shot dead in 2006,
OL,20,Fmonths after admitting he was a police
OL,21,Fand MI5 agent for 20 years.
