OL,3,CBBC reporter tells court she took
OL,4,C'utmost care' with Adams allegation
OL,6,FThe BBC has said the claim was
OL,7,Fcorroborated by five other sources and
OL,8,Fthe reporter involved said the
OL,9,Fconfidential source who made the
OL,10,Fallegation would likely be "killed" if
OL,11,Ftheir identity was revealed.
OL,13,FUnder cross examination by Mr Adams'
OL,14,Fbarrister, Tom Hogan SC, Spotlight
OL,15,Freporter Ms O'Leary said care was
OL,16,Ftaken to corroborate the allegation.
