OL,3,CBBC reporter tells court she took
OL,4,C'utmost care' with Adams allegation
OL,6,FShe said it is "not unusual" in
OL,7,Fjournalism to broadcast an allegation.
OL,9,FMs O'Leary agreed that the word
OL,10,F"sanction" which appears in the
OL,11,Fheadline of the online article, is not
OL,12,Fsaid by Martin in the Spotlight
OL,13,Fprogramme, but said that Martin used
OL,14,Fthe word during his second meeting
OL,15,Fwith her.
OL,17,FShe said it was "not unusual" for a
OL,18,Fheadline to reflect the claims in the
OL,19,Fdetail of the article, but said she
OL,20,Fdid not write the article so could not
OL,21,Fexplain the rationale behind it.
