OL,3,CBBC reporter tells court she took
OL,4,C'utmost care' with Adams allegation
OL,6,FIn relation to an email she sent to a
OL,7,Fproducer on June 22 2016, Ms O'Leary
OL,8,Fwas asked by Mr Hogan why no one could
OL,9,Fbe told about 'Martin'.
OL,11,F"Here was a person who, given what he
OL,12,Fsays he was and given the efforts that
OL,13,Fwe went to in terms of filming the
OL,14,Finterview, and the care that was taken
OL,15,Fwhen meeting him, I didn't want there
OL,16,Fto be chatter," she said.
OL,18,F"It's just a genuine effort to keep
OL,19,Fthings tight out of respect for the
OL,20,Fsource and the story."
