OL,3,CBBC reporter tells court she took
OL,4,C'utmost care' with Adams allegation
OL,6,FIt was put to Ms O'Leary that certain
OL,7,Fvoices were omitted from the programme
OL,8,Fthat were contradicting or were
OL,9,F"taking away from the allegation that
OL,10,Fyou really wanted to make" about Gerry
OL,11,FAdams.
OL,13,FMs O'Leary said: "There was no
OL,14,Fallegation that I really wanted to
OL,15,Fmake."
OL,17,FJudge Alexander Owens said Mr Hogan
OL,18,Fwas suggesting that a statement from
OL,19,Fthe Donaldson family was "yanked" out
OL,20,Fto make the allegation against Mr
OL,21,FAdams "a bit bigger".
