OL,4,C'utmost care' with Adams allegation
OL,6,F"It was in the public interest to
OL,7,Finclude the Adams allegation," she
OL,8,Ftold the court, and added: "Was I to
OL,9,Fignore it?"
OL,11,FShe said there was a need to
OL,12,F"systematically and rigorously" test
OL,13,Fthe allegation, which is why she was
OL,14,Fon the road "non-stop" for months and
OL,15,Fhad met Martin 10 times by the time
OL,16,Fthe programme was broadcast.
OL,18,F"I went out of my way to meet as many
OL,19,Fpeople and sources as I could."
